name: Kim Bradshaw
introduction:
my name is Kim Bradshaw, I'm a natural health activist, and I'm happy to announce that I would like to receive my M.A. in Occupational Therapy from Columbia University.
In my career, I have worked for corporations, government agencies, insurance companies, and many more. Although I have a Bachelor of Science in Business Administration from Columbia University, I am currently looking for a volunteer to help me maintain a smile on my face and to take care of business while I work.
I know how to love telling jokes so I have been looking for people to share my humor with.
